Welcome to the Accounts of the Occult.

Here you will find all the accounts that I have found many curious findings in the world. I have written about the exorcisms of Peter Dane, The Terrors of Calvin Koval, and a myriad of other obscurities that in my opinion, are absolutely bone chilling.

Stay vigilant, stay safe, and be aware that these things are everywhere, so please be kind to yourself and read. Knowledge is the best defense against any unseen foe. You may come across incedents that you couldn't explain before, yet now you will see them with open eyes. You will see the touching of the Old Ones. You will see the Maliciousness of the devil. That being said, there is nothing more fascinating as to learn about why.

Read On. And may the Void keep you.
